text:
<!subteam^S06HNNE4YQ0|@team> It was great to see everyone at All-Hands and Field Day yesterday! Shoutout to everyone who helped make our social a success :) An even bigger shoutout to our eight lovely DTI newbies :yay:  A few quick reminders:
• Please upload your pictures and bios into IDOL so that our website is up-to-date (especially <!subteam^S04Q911MS6A|@newbies>)
• Coffee chat bingo :coffee: has begun, board is bookmarked! Make sure to send in <#CDXU35346|coffee-chats> and submit on IDOL. If you haven't filled out the details form, it's <https://forms.gle/xV2BoKnvMPXiMBEN6|here>!
See you on *10/18 for our next All-Hands* - in the meantime have a fun HOCO and fall break :)
